<br>
This really needs attention.  I don't object at all to the imposed &quot;1 minute of Mana Burn immunity&quot; immediately after the ability has been used on a target, THIS was a necessary measure to insure that &quot;Burn Crews&quot; weren't trivializing content.  However, as it stands now, the ability is completely unjustifiable.<br>
